snippet.title: SunnySide | Meet the Neighbors
snippet.description:
Moving to a new town is never easy, but SunnySide has dozens of residents ready to welcome you. Make friends, visit local hangouts, start relationships and more while running your farm and building your perfect forever home. SunnySide is a pioneering farming and life simulation set in a small diverse Japanese town. 

Ready to start over? Wishlist SunnySide now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1746930/SunnySide/

Follow us on:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/PlaySunnySide
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playsunnyside/
